    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine domini nostri Iehsu Christi eterni dei amen. Anno nativitate eius
                        millesimo centesimo nonagesimo quarto, pridie kal. augusti, indictione
                        duodecima. Ex huius instrumenti pateat edicto quod ego <persName><name
                                ref="Gherarduccius">Gerarduccius</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Teminus">Temini</name></persName> vendo et
                        trado tibi <persName><name ref="Heinricus">Henrigo</name></persName> quondam
                        dicti Temini meam portionem integram que est medietas de una terre petia que
                        vocatur Mons, <rs key="#Wine">vineam</rs> et <rs key="#Fruits/vegetables"
                            >ficas</rs> et <rs key="#Oil">olivas</rs> super se habente, que est
                        posita in plagis et finibus Putei seu in loco ubi dicitur Linari. Et tenet
                        unum caput in <rs key="#Roads">via puplica</rs>, aliud in <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >rivo</rs>, unum laterum in <rs key="#Mountains">monte</rs> quem detinet
                                <persName><name ref="Wido">Guidoni</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Tiniosus">Tiniosi</name></persName> et in monte
                            <persName ref="#people/3217">Aldimarii</persName> quondam <persName
                            ref="#people/3218">Alberti</persName>, aliud in monte <persName><name
                                ref="Merollare">Merollari</name></persName> quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Salomon">Salomoni</name></persName> et in monte dicti
                        Aldimarii. Et est ipsa mea portio duo stariora et medium. (…)
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: solidorum quadraginta bonorum denariorum
                        pisani conii. <foreign>Pena</foreign>: dupli. (…) Actum apud <placeName
                            ref="#places/3210"
                            key="#Rivers #Mountains #Wine #Oil #Fruits/vegetables #Roads"
                            >Puteum</placeName> et ante domum <persName><name ref="Sigerius"
                                >Sigerii</name></persName> et <persName><name ref="Baro"
                                >Baroni</name></persName> germani et quondam <persName><name
                                ref="Rogerius">Rugerii</name></persName>. (…) Presentibus <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Spinellus">Spinello</name></persName> quondam
                                <persName><name ref="Balduinus">Baldovini</name></persName>,
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Villanus">Villano</name></persName>
                        quondam <persName><name ref="Tiniosus">Tiniosi</name></persName> et
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebrandinus"
                            >Ildibrandino</name></persName> filio <persName><name ref="Wizo"
                                >Guictoni</name></persName> rogatis <rs key="#Witness"
                        >testibus</rs>. (S) Ego <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name
                                ref="Hubertus">Ubertus</name></persName> domni imperatoris domni
                        imperatoris <rs key="#Judge">iudex ordinarius</rs> atque <rs key="#Notary"
                            >notarius</rs> post traditam scripsi, complevi et dedi.</ab>
                </div>
